Rules.InvariantScript: LookUp('Appointment Slots' , 'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid).'Meeting Provider'.'Full Name'

ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_location & If(ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_location = 'Appointment Location'.'In Person' , " " & LookUp('Appointment Slots', 'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid).'Location Details'.'Location Name')

If(
    Mod(
        LookUp(
            'Appointment Slots',
            'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
        ).mpa_aptbk_duration,
        60
    ) <> 0, //If Mod 60=0 Mins
    If( //If Mins > 60 Hours w/ decimal
        LookUp(
            'Appointment Slots',
            'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
        ).mpa_aptbk_duration > 60,
        LookUp(
            'Appointment Slots',
            'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
        ).mpa_aptbk_duration / 60 & " Hrs",
        LookUp(
            'Appointment Slots',
            'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
        ).mpa_aptbk_duration & " Min"
    ) & "",
    Mod(//getting the hours
        LookUp(
            'Appointment Slots',
            'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
        ).mpa_aptbk_duration / 60,
        24
    ) <> 0,
    LookUp(
        'Appointment Slots',
        'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
    ).mpa_aptbk_duration / 60 & If(
        LookUp(
            'Appointment Slots',
            'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
        ).mpa_aptbk_duration / 60 = 1,
        " Hr",
        " Hrs"
    ),
    LookUp(//getting the number of days
        'Appointment Slots',
        'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
    ).mpa_aptbk_duration / 60 / 24 & If(
        LookUp(//getting the number of days
            'Appointment Slots',
            'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid
        ).mpa_aptbk_duration / 60 / 24 = 1,
        " Day",
        " Days"
    )
)

Set(varSelectedSlot , LookUp('Appointment Slots', 'Appointment Slot ID' = ThisItem.mpa_aptbk_appointmentslotid));
Navigate('Booking Screen');
